      <title>苏表示失业率仍处于历史低位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-06/su-says-unemployment-is-still-historically-low-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国 11 月份失业率小幅上升至 4.2%，但代理劳工部长朱莉·苏表示，失业率仍处于“历史低位”，经济仍在继续增长。她正在接受“彭博未平仓合约”采访。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-06/su-says-unemployment-is-still-historically-low-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 15:17:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
