      <title>美国消费者信心随通胀预期上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/us-consumer-sentiment-rises-along-with-inflation-expectations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于民主党认为预期关税将带来更大的价格压力风险，美国消费者信心升至 4 月份以来的最高水平，未来一年通胀预期升至五个月高位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/us-consumer-sentiment-rises-along-with-inflation-expectations</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
